<h2 id="win32-api-multithreaded-c-program">Win32 API Multithreaded C Program</h2>

<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/speardragon/save-image-repo/main/img/image-20220926170450607.png" alt="image-20220926170450607" /></p>

